trans-unit.source: Use the `CallTarget` element in your project file to create and execute this task.
trans-unit.target: Använd den `CallTarget` element i projektfilen för att skapa och köra den här åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: For usage and parameter information, see [CallTarget Task](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Användnings- och parametern information finns i [CallTarget uppgift](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.CallTarget"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Tasks.CallTarget"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Instructs the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine to build one or more targets in the current project.
trans-unit.target: Anger den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motor för att skapa en eller flera mål i det aktuella projektet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if all targets built successfully; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om alla mål; har skapats i annat fall <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once per target (<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>) or the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once to build all targets (<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>).
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett booleskt värde som anger om den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motorn anropas en gång per mål (<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>) eller [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motorn anropas en gång för att skapa alla mål (<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once per target; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] engine is called once to build all targets.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motorn anropas en gång per målgrupp. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om den [!INCLUDE[vstecmsbuild](~/add/includes/vstecmsbuild-md.md)] motorn anropas en gång för att skapa alla mål.

trans-unit.source: Gets the outputs of all built targets.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar utdata för alla inbyggda mål.

trans-unit.source: The outputs of all built targets.
Gets or sets the target or targets to build.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger mål eller mål för att skapa.

trans-unit.source: The target or targets to build.
trans-unit.target: Mål eller mål för att skapa.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether the MSBuild engine will return the built targets from the cache.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett booleskt värde som anger om MSBuild-motorn returnera inbyggd mål från cachen.

trans-unit.source: The scope of built targets in the cash is (ProjectFileName, GlobalProperties)[TargetNames] as a list of build items.
trans-unit.target: Omfattningen av inbyggd mål i kontanter är (ProjectFileName GlobalProperties) [TargetNames] som en lista över build-objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the MSBuild engine will return the built targets from the cache; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om MSBuild-motorn returnerar inbyggd mål från cache; i annat fall <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
